data.description: ******** MOTIVATED SELLERS*******Welcome to beautiful Walland, Tennessee! This stunning home offers an unparalleled living experience on over an acre of land. With 4 bedrooms, 3 1/2 baths, and a sprawling 4,800 square feet of living space(Main level 2,500, Basement 2,300), this move-in ready residence is perfect for those seeking both comfort and luxury.As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the attention to detail and the abundance of natural light that fills every corner. The spacious living areas flow seamlessly, providing ample room for relaxation and entertainment. The highlight of this entertainer's paradise is undoubtedly the incredible movie theatre. With a massive screen, reclining leather seats, and acoustic sound walls, you'll feel like you're in a private cinema. All you need to bring is the popcorn!After enjoying a movie night, why not head over to the full custom bar for more fun? This well-appointed space is perfect for hosting friends and family, creating lasting memories and laughter. The possibilities are endless in this private home.Despite its secluded setting, this residence is conveniently located close to everything you need. Just a few miles away, you'll find the breathtaking Foothills Parkway, inviting you to explore its scenic vistas. Also nearby is Blackberry Farm, Blount Memorial Hospital, Maryville College, Townsend, and the Great Smoky Mountains National Park. Nature enthusiasts will be delighted by the abundant wildlife that surrounds the area.As you step outside, you'll be greeted by a generously sized wrap-around deck, offering nearly 1,000 square feet of outdoor living space. This is the perfect spot to bask in the tranquility of your surroundings, whether you're enjoying a morning coffee or hosting a summer barbecue.And let's not forget the black gunite inground pool, where you can cool off on hot summer days and create lasting memories with loved ones. This home truly embodies the spirit of outdoor living and relaxation.Don't miss the opportunity to make this home your own or an income generated property. Give me a call today to schedule your private showing and experience the beauty and endless possibilities that await you in Walland, Tennessee.
